column5: Hi all, Just ordered my couple of tickets for Jays/Baltimore game on Sept 21/09; casting for a cure night. Came up at $16 each..(plus service charges of course)...should be a good night with Dave mingling in the crowd. Imagine a whole section of fishing nuts! Anyone else order tickets?
Wish I could make it - but the wife isn't into Baseball - she find's it to be EXTREMELY BORING next to CURLING!  LOL - Maybe I should bring my other Girlfriend!
